e benefits rather than just features, include neighborhood context, and write at the appropriate tone for luxury vs. entry-level properties. The tool produces genuinely good first drafts that require minimal editing, not AI slop that sounds generic. For agents doing 3-5+ listings per month, the time savings are significant."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-green-400","children":"Pros"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-1.5","children":[["$","li","Produces genuinely good copy, not generic AI filler",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Produces genuinely good copy, not generic AI filler"]}],["$","li","Saves 30-60 minutes per listing",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"Saves 30-60 minutes per listing"]}],["$","li","Understands real estate marketing conventions",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"U