"Lofty (rebranded from Chime in 2023) is one of the most comprehensive real estate technology platforms available. The AI engine powers everything from lead scoring (predicting which leads are most likely to transact soon) to automated follow-up sequences that mimic natural conversation. The platform includes a full IDX website, CRM, dialer, and marketing automation — replacing 3-4 separate tools. Their AI assistant 'Aisha' can handle initial lead qualification conversations via text before handing off to an agent. For teams doing significant lead volume, Lofty's automation is the difference between following up with 100% of leads versus the industry average of 40-50%."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-green-400","children":"Pros"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-1.5","children":[["$","li","All-in-one platform reduces tool sprawl",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"All-in-one platform reduces tool sprawl"]}],["$","li","AI lead scoring genuinely improves conversion rates",{"className":"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-white/70","children":[["$","svg",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400","fill":"currentColor","viewBox":"0 0 20 20","children":["$","path",null,{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z","clipRule":"evenodd"}]}],"AI lead scoring genuinely improves conversion rates"]}],["$","li","AI text assistant handles first-touch lead qualification 24/7",{"cla