or document analysis and long emails. ChatGPT for image analysis and high-volume content. Both for general drafting."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":2}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Test with your actual work",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Spend 30 minutes generating content you actually need and compare. Your preferences will emerge quickly."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":3}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Consider the subscription cost",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Claude Pro is $20/month; ChatGPT Plus is $20/month. Many agents use both ($40/month total) — lower than one dedicated real estate tool."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":4}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Data privacy",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Neither consumer plan should be used with confidential client information. Consider enterprise tiers if you're processing client personal data."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#059669]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#059669]","children":5}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Supplement with specialized tools",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"General AI handles 80% of tasks. For listing descriptions specifically, Listing AI produces better output. For lead qualification, Structurely is better. Know when to use which tool."}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","details","0",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Which is better for writing real estate listing descriptions — ChatGPT or Claude?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"In our testing, ChatGPT (GPT-4o) produces slightly better listing descriptions due to its better image analysis — it can look at property photos and incorporate visual details. Claude produces better long-form prose quality. For best results, use a purpose-built tool like Listing AI, which outperforms both general tools for this specific task."}]]}],["$","details","1",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Can I use AI to analyze real estate contracts?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Claude excels at this due to its 200K context window handling long contracts in one pass. It can summarize key terms, flag unusual clauses, and explain legal language in plain English. Neither AI should be used as legal advice — but using AI to get a quick plain-English summary before reviewing with your broker or attorney is a legitimate time-saver."}]]}],["$","details","2",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Which AI tool is better for real estate email follow-up?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Both are excellent for drafting follow-up emails. Claude tends to write more natural, less formulaic prose. ChatGPT's structured output style works well for more formal communications. The best approach is to use your CRM's built-in AI drafting for routine follow-ups and ChatGPT/Claude for more complex or high-stakes client communications."}]]}],["$","details","3",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Can AI help me prepare for listing appointments?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Yes. Use AI to generate a comparative market analysis narrative, prepare talking points about neighborhood trends, anticipate objections and draft responses, and create a custom presentation outline for the specific property and seller profile. This is one of the highest-ROI uses of general AI for real estate professionals."}]]}],["$","details","4",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["How should I use AI for social media content as a real estate agent?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"AI excels at batch-generating social content: create 30 posts in one session rather than one daily. Provide property details and request varied content types (educational, market updates, local lifestyle, testimonial formats). Review and customize with local knowledge before posting — generic social content doesn't build genuine authority."}]]}],["$","details","5",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Is it ethical to use AI for real estate communications?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Yes, with transparency. The communication should be accurate and represent your genuine perspective — AI drafts it, you review and own it. Don't use AI to mass-send communications you haven't reviewed. Don't use AI to make representations you can't stand behind. The ethical standard is the same as any communication: you're responsible for its accuracy."}]]}],["$","details","6",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#059669]","children":["Which AI tool is better for analyzing real estate market data?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"ChatGPT's Advanced Data Analysis (Code I